OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA milder
OL,6,Fnight tonight, with cloud and rain
OL,7,Fspreading slowly southeast across all
OL,8,Fareas, the rain will become heavy over
OL,9,Fwestern hills with gusty winds.
OL,10,FClearer skies and showers follow from
OL,11,Fthe northwest later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FRain continues to push
OL,14,Fsouthwards, lingering across the
OL,15,Fsoutheast all day. Sunny spells
OL,16,Falready across the northwest becoming
OL,17,Fmore widespread, with blustery
OL,18,Fshowers, these turning wintry mainly
OL,19,Fover northern hills.
